{"tid":337114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［別讓他跑了］郭台銘與特朗普共同宣布 富士康投資100億美元在美設廠","createTime":"2017-07-27T04:28:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T16:28:27.000Z","uid":48083,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"931496fb20b90c93e60301f2ff39edcb6540b26a","tid":337114,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:28:38.000Z","msg":"台灣鴻海集團總裁郭台銘到白宮，與美國總統特朗普共同宣布，鴻海旗下的蘋果手機主要製造商富士康，於未來四年將投資100億美元，在威斯康星州開設世界最先進的8K液晶顯示面板廠，聘請3000名工人，未來規模更可能增至1,3000人，成為美國歷來最大規模的外資投資計劃。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n特朗普就任以來首次邀請海外企業家到白宮出席記者會。郭台銘以英文致詞，感謝特朗普的女婿及白宮高級顧問庫什納，協助他投資美國「飛鷹計劃」翱翔。特朗普就稱讚他的投資擦亮了「美國製造」的招牌，說如果並非自己當選美國總統，郭台銘就不會在美國投資一百億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.memehk.com/posts/18405\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.memehk.com%2Fposts%2F18405&d=i%2FBtsbR%2B2N2Z0f5SNhoUdP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=faf5ae0b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.memehk.com/posts/18405</a>"},{"pid":"9d98a90bda1ca70f60158decaf7cc5be97bc341d","tid":337114,"uid":52819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T05:16:11.000Z","msg":"美國工人同大陸工人將會有差天共地既待遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9c93f02292f78673948ffc6c1babe5516e5be24","tid":337114,"uid":52215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T05:20:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國工人同大陸工人將會有差天共地既待遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一日做六個鐘<br />\n兩個鐘lunch一個鐘tea<br />\n慢慢做<br />\n又到處有零食咖啡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e75f72b46d7605a7128c4873a3202f8d5a2635c","tid":337114,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T05:22:35.000Z","msg":"釜底抽薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4304d4145f6a508c8291b37707aee1557efcf730","tid":337114,"uid":37498,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T05:23:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><block